content: इभ्य {%<ab>a.</ab>%} [इभं गजमर्हति यत्] {@--1@} Wealthy, opulent, rich; <ls>Dk. 41.</ls> {@--2@} Belonging to one's servants (<ab>Ved.</ab>). --भ्यः {@--1@} A king. {@--2@} An elephant-driver. {@--3@} An enemy or foe (<ls>Sāy.</ls>). --भ्या {@--1@} A female elephant. {@--2@} <ab>N.</ab> of the Olibanum tree, Boswellia Serrata.
